title: Spy Game (Collector's Edition) (MKV)
description:
R | 2h 6min | Action, Crime, Thriller | November 21st 2001




Retiring CIA agent Nathan Muir recalls his training of Tom Bishop while working against agency politics to free him from his Chinese captors.



Director: Tony Scott

Writers: Michael Frost Beckner (story), Michael Frost Beckner (screenplay)

Stars: Robert Redford, Brad Pitt, Catherine McCormack



English and French audio, English and Spanish subtitles.

Feature commentaries with the director and producers.

Anamorphic Widescreen 2.35:1
